OL,3,CCash is king for holidaymakers, survey
OL,4,Cshows
OL,6,FPeople are more likely to pay for
OL,7,Fitems with cash when they are on
OL,8,Fholiday overseas compared with when
OL,9,Fthey are in the UK, a new survey
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FSome 44% of consumers polled said they
OL,13,Fuse cash more on foreign trips,
OL,14,Fcompared with 7% who said they use it
OL,15,Fless.
OL,17,FThe most common reason given for using
OL,18,Fcash instead of card on holiday is
OL,19,Fthat it is the only form of payment
OL,20,Faccepted at the destinations they are
OL,21,Fvisiting (44%).
