OL,3,CCash is king for holidaymakers, survey
OL,4,Cshows
OL,6,FOther reasons are to help manage how
OL,7,Fmuch they spend while away (37%), to
OL,8,Favoid bank charges and ATM fees (28%),
OL,9,Fand fears over card details being
OL,10,Fstolen (21%).
OL,12,FAbta recommends that people take some
OL,13,Fcash with them on holiday so they know
OL,14,Fthey can pay for things if needed
OL,15,Fwithout having to resort to ATM
OL,16,Fwithdrawals, which often incur hefty
OL,17,Fcharges.
