OL,3,CCash is king for holidaymakers, survey
OL,4,Cshows
OL,6,FIt warned that consumers face fees of
OL,7,Fbetween two euros (#1.66) and six
OL,8,Feuros (#4.98) every time they take out
OL,9,Fcash from a machine when visiting
OL,10,Fcountries such as Spain, Greece and
OL,11,FItaly, with currency conversion
OL,12,Fcharges added on top.
OL,14,FIn some destinations such as Germany,
OL,15,Fcash is more widely accepted in bars
OL,16,Fand restaurants than credit or debit
OL,17,Fcards.
