OL,3,CCash is king for holidaymakers, survey
OL,4,Cshows
OL,6,FAbta director of communications Graeme
OL,7,FBuck said: "For many travelling
OL,8,Fabroad, our research suggests that
OL,9,Fcash is still king when it comes to
OL,10,Fspending on holiday.
OL,12,F"Standard payment types vary from
OL,13,Fcountry to country, so it is essential
OL,14,Fto make sure you take enough travel
OL,15,Fmoney as you may find you need, or
OL,16,Fprefer, to pay with cash.
OL,18,F"Having foreign currency makes for a
OL,19,Fmore convenient, stress-free holiday."
